{"tid":646350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川男墮橋遭竹枝插入臀","createTime":"2018-04-29T03:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T06:15:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5383d6baeee212b8e5cbc03b4cf3cc429de60c09","tid":646350,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】（星島日報報道）四川遂寧市一名男子近日過路天橋上安裝廣告牌時，不慎摔下直墮花槽，被下方一根竹直插臀部受傷。消防接報到場後先將竹子鋸斷，之後再將他送院救治。現場視頻所見，竹子插入男子臀部頗深，男子狀甚痛苦，連趴在單架上都不行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E7%94%B7%E5%A2%AE%E6%A9%8B%E9%81%AD%E7%AB%B9%E6%9E%9D%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E8%87%80-221117718.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B7%259D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A9%258B%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E6%259E%259D%25E6%258F%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%2587%2580-221117718.html&d=%2B9OPQEDzr2OMqe7q0QsGlG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c9d806fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E7%94%B7%E5%A2%AE%E6%A9%8B%E9%81%AD%E7%AB%B9%E6%9E%9D%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E8%87%80-221117718.html</a>"},{"pid":"41133e3815612950bdb33410e9e43a15f0057f65","tid":646350,"uid":86508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:42:59.000Z","msg":"相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627823e939154e82149fe061e0110ecb4dd75b5a","tid":646350,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"屎忽撞棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9767de0bb593a815fd96e81a3caa3f65c53635ea","tid":646350,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41133e3815612950bdb33410e9e43a15f0057f65","tid":646350,"uid":86508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:42:59.000Z","msg":"相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" clas